@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/jibble
@apiSecret = 5056a049365ca0fd1561acb1ead2887b9aae3743667bdd0b7f977ef7f92c2889

### Health check (sin autenticación)
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### 0. DEBUG: Verificar que la autenticación con Jibble funciona
GET {{baseUrl}}/debug/token
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

###

### 0b. STATUS: Ver ventana de fichaje, empleados fichados, auto clock-out
GET {{baseUrl}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

###

### 1. Crear un empleado nuevo
POST {{baseUrl}}/employees
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "fullName": "pepe  garcia",
  "email": "juan.pere@empresa.com"
}

###

### 2. Obtener lista de empleados → copia el campo `id` como personId
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

###

### 3. Obtener lista de actividades → copia el campo `id` como activityId (ej: Work, Break)
GET {{baseUrl}}/activities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

###

### Registrar entrada (clock-in) de un empleado
POST {{baseUrl}}/clock-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "personId": "0dcfc065-f333-44e0-a96e-5a55d831ab7b",
  "activityId": ""
}

###

### Registrar entrada (clock-in) sin actividad
POST {{baseUrl}}/clock-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "personId": "422c11d8-90f6-4e99-a0b0-9cc854c03147"
}

###

### Registrar salida (clock-out) de un empleado
POST {{baseUrl}}/clock-out
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "personId": "422c11d8-90f6-4e99-a0b0-9cc854c03147"
}

###

### ⚡ Forzar clock-IN a todos los empleados sin entrada hoy (igual que el cron de las 8:00)
POST {{baseUrl}}/clock-in-all
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

###

### Iniciar descanso (break-in)
POST {{baseUrl}}/break-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "personId": "422c11d8-90f6-4e99-a0b0-9cc854c03147"
}

###

### Finalizar descanso (break-out)
POST {{baseUrl}}/break-out
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

{
  "personId": "422c11d8-90f6-4e99-a0b0-9cc854c03147"
}

###

### Obtener registros de asistencia (rango de fechas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-20
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiSecret}}

